'''Akmal Vladimirovich Mozgovoy''' ({{langx|uz|Akmal Mozgovoy}}; born 2 April 1999) is an Uzbek professional  [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Pakhtakor FC|Pakhtakor]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].<ref>{{NFT player|79189|access-date=4 March 2021}}</ref><ref>{{soccerway|akmal-mozgovoy/534313|accessdate=4 March 2021}}</ref>

==Career==
===International===
Mozgovoy made his debut for the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]] main team on 3 September 2020 in a [[Friendly (sport)|Friendly]] match against [[Tajikistan national football team|Tajikistan]].<ref>[https://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/27778/Uzbekistan_Tajikistan.html Uzbekistan 2–1 Tajikistan]</ref>

